                     <interp inst="t18280410-50-person422" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was present at the prisoner's marriage to 
               <persName id="t18280410-50-victim423" type="victimName">
                  George 
                  Kempson
               <interp inst="t18280410-50-victim423" type="surname" value="Kempson"></interp>
